_OMAKO_ 		...	reduces menus to fit on a phone screen
_NANONOTE_		...	adds keyboard (instead of pointer-based) input for everything 
POSIX					... necessary for file I/O 
GTKGUI				... GUI (Gtk+2 - based), necessary for actual use
